The '''2005-06 [[Romanian Women's Cup|Cupa României]]''' was the 3rd annual Romanian women's [[Association football|football]] knockout tournaments.<ref>[http://rsssf.com/tablesr/roem-wom06.html RSSSF]</ref> 
