[[Korfball]] was a [[demonstration sport]] at the [[1920 Summer Olympics|1920 Olympic Games]] in [[Antwerp]]. It took place at the [[Olympisch Stadion (Antwerp)|Olympisch Stadion]] at 22 August 1920.<ref>[http://home.scarlet.be/~fhermans/antwerpen1920/uitslagen.html Olympische Spelen - Antwerpen 1920]</ref><ref>[http://www.knkv.nl/userfiles/knkv_corporate/KNKV_Vademecum_Historisch_Overzicht.pdf BEKNOPT HISTORISCH OVERZICHT KORFBAL IN (K)NKB/KNKV]</ref><ref>[http://www.la84foundation.org/SportsLibrary/JOH/JOHv2n2/JOHv2n2f.pdf KORFBALL AT THE OLYMPIC GAMES]</ref>
It was the first appearance of korfball at the Olympic Games.
